<h2>Growl Cappuccino</h2>
------------------

<h3>What is StropheCappuccino ?</h3>
---------------------------
<p>This is a framework that allows to mimic Growl notificatiom system in Cappuccino</p>

<h3>Quick Start</h3>
-----------
<p>Simply include the GrowlCappuccino framework in your Frameworks directory and include GrowlCappuccino.js</p>
<code>
@import <GrowlCappuccino/GrowlCappuccino.j>

[...]

var growl = [TNGrowlCenter defaultCenter];

[grow setView:aView];
[growl pushNotificationWithTitle:@"Hello" message:@"Hello World!"];

[...]
</code>

<h3>Documentation</h3>
<p>To generate the documentation execute the following :</p>

# doxygen GrowlCappuccino.doxygen
